        <li>Higher price than Copy.ai</li>
        <li>Fewer templates than Copy.ai</li>
        <li>Less flexible workflows</li>
        <li>Free tier only 7-day trial</li>
        <li>Learning curve for advanced features</li>
        <li>Some integrations still maturing</li>
        
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>Copy.ai Pros</h3>
    <div class="pros-box">
