        <li>Active development and frequent updates</li>
        <li>Growing community and ecosystem</li>
        
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>Copy.ai Cons</h3>
    <div class="cons-box">
      <ul>
        <li>Less polished marketing copy</li>
        <li>Brand voice less consistent</li>
        <li>Fewer SEO features</li>
        <li>More editing required</li>
        <li>Less suitable for enterprise teams</li>
        <li>Interface can feel overwhelming initially</li>
        <li>Premium features require higher tier plans</li>
        
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Who Should Use Which?</h2>
    <p><strong>Choose Jasper AI</strong> if marketing copy quality and brand consistency are your priorities.</p>
    <p><strong>Choose Copy.ai</strong> if you need fast content generation, workflow automation, and a lower price point.</p>

    <h2>Real-World Use Cases</h2>

      <div class="use-case">
    <h3>Marketing Teams</h3>
    <p>Jasper brand voice and SEO features make it better for professional marketing content.</p>
  </div>
    <div class="use-case">
    <h3>Solo Creators</h3>
    <p>Copy.ai lower price and generous free tier make it more accessible for individual creators.</p>
  </div>
    <div class="use-case">
